![](https://virtnetwork.com/images/logo.png)

Hi! Thank you for taking the opportunity to see our ad!

VirtNetwork Solutions is delighted to celebrate our opening launch with some exclusive plans for the LowEndTalk Community. We have put a lot of time, effort, and hard work into building our company and hope that you can see and experience the difference. Our core focus here at VirtNetwork is all about quality service and stellar customer support at affordable prices. All services are hosted at ColoCrossing's Buffalo, New York datacenter and utilize ColoCrossing's premium network comprised of tier-1 bandwidth carriers.

Our specifications are NO JOKE. We use: &lt;br&gt;

Dual Intel Xeon X5650 Hex Core Processors &lt;br&gt;
4x 3TB WD RE4 SATA II Drives &lt;br&gt;
LSI 9271-4i Hardware RAID-10 with Cachevault &lt;br&gt;
96GB DDR3 ECC Registered Memory &lt;br&gt;
1Gbit Dedicated Uplink Port &lt;br&gt;
.. virtualizated with KVM &lt;br&gt;

You are GUARANTEED: &lt;br&gt;
- NON-OVERSOLD Disk Space / RAM resources &lt;br&gt;
- High Quality Hosting, Hardware, and Network &lt;br&gt;
- _CLEAN / Non-Blacklisted IPv4 Addresses_ &lt;br&gt;
- 24/7 Technical Support &lt;br&gt;
- 100% Satisfaction &lt;br&gt;
- 99.99% Uptime &lt;br&gt;
- Unsure about our services?  We have a **60-Days Unconditional MONEY BACK GUARANTEE** &lt;br&gt;
- NO BULL! We are SERIOUS about our hosting &lt;br&gt;

Our Plans:

