&gt; 5000GB Monthly Bandwidth
&gt; 1Gbit Port Uplink
&gt; 5 IPv4 Addresses

Monthly Cost: $7.00 per month

2. **Special KVM Plan Mini** - [Order Link](https://virtnetwork.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=18)

